<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wygeleis, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der ii<hi rend="sup">c</hi>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das haben wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigiste<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs, brief <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sind, daran uns sein
                                <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan> und gepewt, dem edeln
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Coldicz,
                        die <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ii<hi rend="sup">c</hi>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> zu geben, dem auch uns gebürt gehorsam darinn
                        zu sein, als ir selbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt. Wo wir
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> sust lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> kathedra Petri.</ab>
</div>
